	"system": {
		"description": "<p>You are an expert in underhanded tactics and chicanery, clever even by the standards of the underworld. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p>Your Dexterity, Intelligence, or Charisma score increases by +1, to a maximum of 20.</p></li><li><p>You gain proficiency with the Deception, Sleight of Hand, or Stealth skill. If you are already proficient with all three, you gain an expertise die to one of your choice.</p></li><li><p>You gain proficiency with your choice of one combat tradition from the following list: Mist and Shade, Mirror’s Glint, Viper’s Fangs, or Grinding Cog. You learn a maneuver from the selected tradition of a degree that you can learn. It does not count against your maneuvers known.</p></li><li><p>When you use the Dash action (whether normally or via Cunning Action) your movement speed increases by 10 feet for the dash.</p></li><li><p>You gain the services of an Inexperienced Footpad follower. It does not count against your maximum followers total.</p></li></ul>",
